{"version":3,"kind":"Notebook","sha256":"0e9e32f576ad263fc74c3322b266a63916973fe5ee7c4b572bc5aa64a58d02e8","slug":"chapter02-sec02","location":"/chapter02/chapter02_sec02.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"2.2 Fotoaufnahme in der Praxis","kernelspec":{"name":"python3","display_name":"Python 3"},"content_includes_title":false,"authors":[{"id":"Simone Gramsch","name":"Simone Gramsch"}],"open_access":true,"license":{"content":{"id":"CC-BY-NC-SA-4.0","url":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/","name":"Creative Commons Attribution Non Commercial Share Alike 4.0 International","CC":true}},"github":"https://github.com/gramschs/thma_virtual_engineering","numbering":{"title":{"offset":1}},"source_url":"https://github.com/gramschs/thma_virtual_engineering/blob/main/chapter02/chapter02_sec02.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/gramschs/thma_virtual_engineering/edit/main/chapter02/chapter02_sec02.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"chapter02_sec02.md","url":"/thma_virtual_engineering/build/chapter02_sec02-90ce25dd3d916ff82b18113ebabca49f.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ein gutes 3D-Modell steht und fällt mit der Qualität der Fotos. Meshroom kann\naus schlechten Aufnahmen kein gutes Modell berechnen. In diesem Kapitel lernen\nwir, worauf es bei der Fotoaufnahme ankommt: von der Wahl der\nKameraeinstellungen über die Aufnahmestrategie bis hin zum Umgang mit\nschwierigen Oberflächen.","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"Vczf713ycW"}],"key":"fKhfUTRgNc"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lernziele","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"JkhvttGAJV"}],"identifier":"lernziele","label":"Lernziele","html_id":"lernziele","implicit":true,"key":"ExAwGsxIiE"},{"type":"admonition","children":[{"type":"admonitionTitle","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lernziele","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"PecFjGAGBW"}],"key":"WebI3RUHN3"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sie kennen die wichtigsten Kameraeinstellungen für eine gute\nPhotogrammetrie-Aufnahme und können diese begründen.","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"f6dALFU93a"}],"key":"koIQN2ARAq"}],"checked":false,"key":"SeIV17EENS"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sie können eine geeignete Aufnahmestrategie für ein kompaktes Objekt\nplanen und die Mindestanzahl an Fotos sowie den erforderlichen Überlappungsgrad\nbenennen.","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"UcCYbgcy4n"}],"key":"Ig7H598pwj"}],"checked":false,"key":"hqp1LelsQ1"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sie wissen, wie Sie mit schwierigen Oberflächen umgehen, und kennen\nden Einsatz von Mattierungsspray als Workaround.","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"key":"dmfUayFu5I"}],"key":"yBuCSiZkIN"}],"checked":false,"key":"VA9fg1GQpi"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sie können typische Aufnahmefehler benennen und erklären, wie diese\ndie Rekonstruktionsqualität beeinflussen.","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"JWBTpaRZAU"}],"key":"HecongtDK5"}],"checked":false,"key":"MMkbFfQs55"}],"key":"nrccVzKOP5"}],"class":"attention","key":"wTYCNmfLpI"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Kameraeinstellungen","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"key":"H5Z1F7APX8"}],"identifier":"kameraeinstellungen","label":"Kameraeinstellungen","html_id":"kameraeinstellungen","implicit":true,"key":"pXvVum6Tz8"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Für die Photogrammetrie ist keine Profikamera notwendig. Ein modernes\nSmartphone liefert in den meisten Fällen ausreichende Ergebnisse. Entscheidend\nist jedoch, dass die Kameraeinstellungen während der gesamten Aufnahmesession\nkonstant bleiben und die Bilder scharf und gut belichtet sind.","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"key":"Ds1DPOulFW"}],"key":"bnriz1AlBe"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":54,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Fokus","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"eiuEMtFxtU"}],"key":"drMRbRZsQP"},{"type":"text","value":": Der Autofokus sollte deaktiviert oder auf das Objekt fixiert\nwerden. Wenn der Fokus zwischen den Aufnahmen wechselt, verändert sich die\nscheinbare Größe von Merkmalspunkten, was die Zuordnung erschwert. Bei\nSmartphones lässt sich der Fokus in der Regel durch langes Drücken auf das\nObjekt im Bildschirm fixieren.","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"dtXghYak2t"}],"key":"xr8QKdwu9g"}],"key":"nTVzq43Tg5"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Belichtung","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"key":"SfcI4Lm6Ti"}],"key":"pjmShd1Cca"},{"type":"text","value":": Die automatische Belichtungsanpassung sollte ebenfalls\ndeaktiviert werden. Wechselnde Helligkeitswerte von Bild zu Bild erschweren die\nMerkmalszuordnung erheblich. Ziel ist eine gleichmäßige, leicht unterbelichtete\nAufnahme, da überbelichtete Bereiche keine Texturinformation mehr enthalten.","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"key":"DL7ahxSVP4"}],"key":"ydKlH8Xflx"}],"key":"Pitdpco2yR"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":49,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ISO-Wert","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"key":"BXILyaQUCi"}],"key":"bS6swc14hy"},{"type":"text","value":": Ein niedriger ISO-Wert (ISO 100 bis 400) reduziert das\nBildrauschen. Rauschen erzeugt zufällige Helligkeitsschwankungen auf der\nOberfläche, die der Algorithmus fälschlicherweise als Merkmalspunkte\ninterpretieren kann.","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"key":"JDqwR8aAyp"}],"key":"IMF6JD10wV"}],"key":"omLOJJezGn"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Auflösung","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"key":"VbZzPCWWAJ"}],"key":"Psp9BdOp81"},{"type":"text","value":": Die höchste verfügbare Auflösung verwenden. Mehr Pixel bedeuten\nmehr potenzielle Merkmalspunkte und damit ein detaillierteres Ergebnis.","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"key":"r7AZoOvdSv"}],"key":"C7145k6Jh3"}],"key":"Aq3W03DLOU"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1},"end":{"line":54,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1},"end":{"line":52,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Blitz","position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1},"end":{"line":52,"column":1}},"key":"W9x2RotLRF"}],"key":"SjXwhZLjq0"},{"type":"text","value":": Den Blitz ausschalten. Blitzlicht erzeugt harte Schatten und\nReflexionen, die die Oberflächentextur verfälschen.","position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1},"end":{"line":52,"column":1}},"key":"wVQ4j19sU3"}],"key":"vqMSSumj2w"}],"key":"RiOvc5rYRR"}],"key":"ZzTTOHo0Fk"},{"type":"admonition","children":[{"type":"admonitionTitle","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mini-Übung","position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1},"end":{"line":55,"column":1}},"key":"fXC7zCzsRj"}],"key":"SoVyy5HD7x"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1},"end":{"line":60,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Warum ist es problematisch, wenn die automatische Belichtung zwischen zwei\naufeinanderfolgenden Fotos die Helligkeit anpasst? Überlegen Sie, was das\nkonkret für die Merkmalszuordnung in SfM bedeutet, und notieren Sie Ihre\nAntwort in zwei bis drei Sätzen.","position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1},"end":{"line":57,"column":1}},"key":"HvR0JYpUmy"}],"key":"DpmcYmWeuT"}],"class":"tip","key":"EPoncqg9St"},{"type":"admonition","children":[{"type":"admonitionTitle","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lösung","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"key":"eSDt7NJ2El"}],"key":"u0jf9neZIq"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":66,"column":1},"end":{"line":72,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wenn die Belichtung zwischen zwei Fotos wechselt, verändern sich die\nHelligkeitswerte derselben Oberflächenpunkte. Ein Merkmalspunkt, der auf\nFoto 1 einen bestimmten Helligkeitswert hat, sieht auf Foto 2 anders aus,\nobwohl es sich um denselben Punkt handelt. Der SfM-Algorithmus kann diesen\nPunkt dann nicht mehr zuverlässig zuordnen, was zu einer geringeren Anzahl\nkorrekt gematchter Merkmalspunkte und damit zu einer schlechteren oder\nfehlerhaften Rekonstruktion führt.","position":{"start":{"line":66,"column":1},"end":{"line":66,"column":1}},"key":"SjipSD5km2"}],"key":"KwW9oDWDZe"}],"class":"tip dropdown","key":"mnTPuKdDNf"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":75,"column":1},"end":{"line":75,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Aufnahmestrategie","position":{"start":{"line":75,"column":1},"end":{"line":75,"column":1}},"key":"pMLwbhXGU0"}],"identifier":"aufnahmestrategie","label":"Aufnahmestrategie","html_id":"aufnahmestrategie","implicit":true,"key":"e9TUueU8ie"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":77,"column":1},"end":{"line":80,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Die räumliche Anordnung der Fotos rund um das Objekt ist mindestens genauso\nwichtig wie die Kameraeinstellungen. Wir folgen einer systematischen\nStrategie, die sicherstellt, dass jede Stelle des Objekts aus mindestens drei\nverschiedenen Winkeln fotografiert wird.","position":{"start":{"line":77,"column":1},"end":{"line":77,"column":1}},"key":"AdhXOiXTV0"}],"key":"a8l84HCQcJ"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":82,"column":1},"end":{"line":111,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":82,"column":1},"end":{"line":85,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":82,"column":1},"end":{"line":85,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":82,"column":1},"end":{"line":82,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Überlappung","position":{"start":{"line":82,"column":1},"end":{"line":82,"column":1}},"key":"xpRdgCejx4"}],"key":"SARAn48mqT"},{"type":"text","value":": Benachbarte Fotos sollten sich zu mindestens 60 bis 80\nProzent überlappen. Zu wenig Überlappung bedeutet, dass der Algorithmus nicht\ngenug gemeinsame Merkmalspunkte zwischen benachbarten Fotos findet und die\nKamerapositionen nicht korrekt berechnen kann.","position":{"start":{"line":82,"column":1},"end":{"line":82,"column":1}},"key":"z5QhHtBUcS"}],"key":"wD0NOGJzQu"}],"key":"E99Zr7MfS0"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":86,"column":1},"end":{"line":88,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":86,"column":1},"end":{"line":88,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":86,"column":1},"end":{"line":86,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Anzahl der Fotos","position":{"start":{"line":86,"column":1},"end":{"line":86,"column":1}},"key":"iA6FqKPPI1"}],"key":"IDWxVaa7jD"},{"type":"text","value":": Für ein kompaktes Objekt (ca. 10 bis 30 cm) empfehlen\nwir mindestens 60 bis 80 Fotos. Mehr Fotos verbessern die Qualität, erhöhen aber\nauch die Rechenzeit.","position":{"start":{"line":86,"column":1},"end":{"line":86,"column":1}},"key":"kxdatBBhDz"}],"key":"bjoPt4j5Kp"}],"key":"n7gCfYRwsO"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":89,"column":1},"end":{"line":100,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":89,"column":1},"end":{"line":93,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":89,"column":1},"end":{"line":89,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mehrere Ebenen","position":{"start":{"line":89,"column":1},"end":{"line":89,"column":1}},"key":"uJdj5Axt3P"}],"key":"lrPAvEiuHd"},{"type":"text","value":": Wir fotografieren das Objekt in mindestens zwei\nhorizontalen Ebenen: einmal auf Höhe des Objekts (horizontale Umrundung) und\neinmal von leicht oben (ca. 30 bis 45 Grad). Falls das Objekt eine Unterseite\nhat, wird auch diese aus einer dritten Ebene aufgenommen. Eine bewährte\nAufnahmestrategie für ein kompaktes Objekt sieht so aus:","position":{"start":{"line":89,"column":1},"end":{"line":89,"column":1}},"key":"BQZ0hXCq8m"}],"key":"ZhwLyWk3ZL"},{"type":"code","lang":"code","value":"Ebene 1 (horizontal):  20-25 Fotos, gleichmäßig um das Objekt verteilt\nEbene 2 (von oben):    20-25 Fotos, gleichmäßig um das Objekt verteilt\nEbene 3 (Nahaufnahmen): 15-20 Fotos von Details, Vertiefungen, Kanten","position":{"start":{"line":95,"column":1},"end":{"line":99,"column":1}},"key":"YcxJLyFHHo"}],"key":"her06pA8rq"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":101,"column":1},"end":{"line":103,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":101,"column":1},"end":{"line":103,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":101,"column":1},"end":{"line":101,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Kamerabewegung","position":{"start":{"line":101,"column":1},"end":{"line":101,"column":1}},"key":"JTgcATpTzi"}],"key":"DNjPhRzV3I"},{"type":"text","value":": Wir bewegen immer die Kamera um das Objekt herum, nicht\ndas Objekt vor der Kamera. Ein sich drehendes Objekt verändert die Beleuchtung\nund damit die Textur auf der Oberfläche, was die Merkmalszuordnung stört.","position":{"start":{"line":101,"column":1},"end":{"line":101,"column":1}},"key":"U1GUhFbigf"}],"key":"VTBtdm5UZh"}],"key":"EZ6NsPC4x1"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":104,"column":1},"end":{"line":107,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":104,"column":1},"end":{"line":107,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":104,"column":1},"end":{"line":104,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hintergrund","position":{"start":{"line":104,"column":1},"end":{"line":104,"column":1}},"key":"hao9cH12jS"}],"key":"cPhIOYVGOe"},{"type":"text","value":": Das Objekt auf einen neutralen, matten Untergrund stellen,\nzum Beispiel auf ein Stück graues Papier oder ein Handtuch. Ein strukturreicher\nHintergrund kann vom Algorithmus mitrekonstruiert werden und das Ergebnis\nverschlechtern.","position":{"start":{"line":104,"column":1},"end":{"line":104,"column":1}},"key":"i60K5DJLgv"}],"key":"gQDlFfH1RG"}],"key":"q6MiVZP8HA"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":108,"column":1},"end":{"line":111,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":108,"column":1},"end":{"line":110,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":108,"column":1},"end":{"line":108,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Beleuchtung","position":{"start":{"line":108,"column":1},"end":{"line":108,"column":1}},"key":"v58lRvGfwg"}],"key":"OcQNPTDduP"},{"type":"text","value":": Diffuses Tageslicht oder gleichmäßige Raumbeleuchtung ist\nideal. Direkte Sonneneinstrahlung erzeugt harte Schatten, die Teile des Objekts\nverdecken und die Rekonstruktion in diesen Bereichen unmöglich machen.","position":{"start":{"line":108,"column":1},"end":{"line":108,"column":1}},"key":"ipNsYdkhpm"}],"key":"tDGp760Ui8"}],"key":"y7IbJqD13i"}],"key":"p5c7vEG9fw"},{"type":"admonition","children":[{"type":"admonitionTitle","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mini-Übung","position":{"start":{"line":112,"column":1},"end":{"line":112,"column":1}},"key":"MUz7tGFFw6"}],"key":"PXpm7YlqRT"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":114,"column":1},"end":{"line":116,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Planen Sie die Fotoaufnahme für das Objekt, das Sie in Übung 1.3 ausgewählt\nhaben. Skizzieren Sie auf einem Blatt Papier, aus welchen Positionen und\nWinkeln Sie fotografieren würden, und beantworten Sie folgende Fragen:","position":{"start":{"line":114,"column":1},"end":{"line":114,"column":1}},"key":"VdUXl2TCXb"}],"key":"hgWVRFjOIZ"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":118,"column":1},"end":{"line":120,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":118,"column":1},"end":{"line":118,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"In wie vielen Ebenen fotografieren Sie?","position":{"start":{"line":118,"column":1},"end":{"line":118,"column":1}},"key":"YWj3IYqZB4"}],"key":"aUi1x4Ft3C"}],"key":"W2IIbI66C9"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":119,"column":1},"end":{"line":119,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wie viele Fotos planen Sie insgesamt?","position":{"start":{"line":119,"column":1},"end":{"line":119,"column":1}},"key":"ClJ10yw5bZ"}],"key":"A9MLVToaXi"}],"key":"IExJDSbCzw"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":120,"column":1},"end":{"line":120,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Welche besonderen Bereiche des Objekts erfordern zusätzliche Nahaufnahmen?","position":{"start":{"line":120,"column":1},"end":{"line":120,"column":1}},"key":"JFU193NnwZ"}],"key":"BkFW86rseR"}],"key":"y5RRMKjsPF"}],"key":"f55Zw07OfS"}],"class":"tip","key":"ND1ZrROTMi"},{"type":"admonition","children":[{"type":"admonitionTitle","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lösung","position":{"start":{"line":123,"column":1},"end":{"line":123,"column":1}},"key":"rePK5s3RLm"}],"key":"FtqoYYrVsd"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":126,"column":1},"end":{"line":126,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Beispiellösung für ein Stirnrad:","position":{"start":{"line":126,"column":1},"end":{"line":126,"column":1}},"key":"mq5wwQMqCD"}],"key":"VPTvtuRYpG"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":128,"column":1},"end":{"line":133,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ebene 1 (horizontal, 0 Grad): 24 Fotos im Abstand von je 15 Grad rund um das\nZahnrad, aus ca. 30 cm Entfernung. Ebene 2 (von oben, ca. 40 Grad): weitere\n24 Fotos aus derselben Entfernung. Da das Zahnrad eine plane Unterseite hat,\nwird es einmal umgedreht und dieselbe Strategie wiederholt, insgesamt also ca.\n60 Fotos für beide Seiten. Zusätzlich ca. 15 Nahaufnahmen der Zahnspalten und\nder zentralen Bohrung, da diese feinen Details mehr Abdeckung benötigen.","position":{"start":{"line":128,"column":1},"end":{"line":128,"column":1}},"key":"UKAXJ7luAb"}],"key":"XBOTPhNF2t"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":135,"column":1},"end":{"line":135,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gesamtanzahl: ca. 75 Fotos.","position":{"start":{"line":135,"column":1},"end":{"line":135,"column":1}},"key":"Oj6C98avS6"}],"key":"Yl2j6o6aiz"}],"class":"tip dropdown","key":"pQkHSNJY4x"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":138,"column":1},"end":{"line":138,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Schwierige Oberflächen und Mattierungsspray","position":{"start":{"line":138,"column":1},"end":{"line":138,"column":1}},"key":"kb5yXMtmw1"}],"identifier":"schwierige-oberfl-chen-und-mattierungsspray","label":"Schwierige Oberflächen und Mattierungsspray","html_id":"schwierige-oberfl-chen-und-mattierungsspray","implicit":true,"key":"pqIF4LE5Oh"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":140,"column":1},"end":{"line":142,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Manche Objekte lassen sich mit der oben beschriebenen Strategie nicht\nzufriedenstellend rekonstruieren, weil ihre Oberfläche für die Photogrammetrie\nungünstig ist. Die häufigsten Problemfälle sind:","position":{"start":{"line":140,"column":1},"end":{"line":140,"column":1}},"key":"ZXL8hDHYwm"}],"key":"cAAAeO90K2"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":144,"column":1},"end":{"line":153,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":144,"column":1},"end":{"line":146,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":144,"column":1},"end":{"line":144,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Glänzende Oberflächen","position":{"start":{"line":144,"column":1},"end":{"line":144,"column":1}},"key":"ECbLgTfZqv"}],"key":"hu5JkfIkW2"},{"type":"text","value":": Poliertes Metall, Glas oder Hochglanzkunststoff\nerzeugen Reflexionen, die sich mit dem Aufnahmewinkel verschieben. Der\nAlgorithmus kann diese Reflexionspunkte nicht stabil zuordnen.","position":{"start":{"line":144,"column":1},"end":{"line":144,"column":1}},"key":"oaYlVNjXsn"}],"key":"tQSjJLhmgc"}],"key":"vjVcshAxAF"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":147,"column":1},"end":{"line":149,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":147,"column":1},"end":{"line":147,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Einfarbige, strukturlose Flächen","position":{"start":{"line":147,"column":1},"end":{"line":147,"column":1}},"key":"PTAlRIsv34"}],"key":"pGqkeU9x1C"},{"type":"text","value":": Eine weiß lackierte Metallfläche oder\neine glatte Keramikoberfläche bietet keine Merkmalspunkte. Der Algorithmus\nfindet dort buchstäblich nichts zum Zuordnen.","position":{"start":{"line":147,"column":1},"end":{"line":147,"column":1}},"key":"kTm6abjs84"}],"key":"hdtxCqnVI1"}],"key":"EyZuSqYeKy"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":150,"column":1},"end":{"line":153,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":150,"column":1},"end":{"line":150,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Transparente Materialien","position":{"start":{"line":150,"column":1},"end":{"line":150,"column":1}},"key":"UIDbNOLc4E"}],"key":"xdmASyajDT"},{"type":"text","value":": Glas oder Acrylglas lässt Licht hindurch und\nreflektiert es gleichzeitig. Das Erscheinungsbild ist winkelabhängig und für\nPhotogrammetrie nahezu unbrauchbar.","position":{"start":{"line":150,"column":1},"end":{"line":150,"column":1}},"key":"ROTp4Urmbw"}],"key":"dXTjR8EhCH"}],"key":"tZV5xXefax"}],"key":"hUeFylmEat"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":154,"column":1},"end":{"line":159,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Die Lösung in der industriellen Praxis ist ","position":{"start":{"line":154,"column":1},"end":{"line":154,"column":1}},"key":"ouRs8QzGQo"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":154,"column":1},"end":{"line":154,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mattierungsspray","position":{"start":{"line":154,"column":1},"end":{"line":154,"column":1}},"key":"vlKMBadEn9"}],"key":"iRIv0RquVP"},{"type":"text","value":" (englisch:\n","position":{"start":{"line":154,"column":1},"end":{"line":154,"column":1}},"key":"sWUp19jad5"},{"type":"emphasis","position":{"start":{"line":154,"column":1},"end":{"line":154,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"scanning spray","position":{"start":{"line":154,"column":1},"end":{"line":154,"column":1}},"key":"zukiK9BscN"}],"key":"FjebVmbzAO"},{"type":"text","value":" oder ","position":{"start":{"line":154,"column":1},"end":{"line":154,"column":1}},"key":"Zq0Qsdr6UE"},{"type":"emphasis","position":{"start":{"line":154,"column":1},"end":{"line":154,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"developer spray","position":{"start":{"line":154,"column":1},"end":{"line":154,"column":1}},"key":"P3uMflDjeX"}],"key":"zcRK2QTeN8"},{"type":"text","value":"). Es handelt sich um einen feinen,\ngleichmäßigen weißen Film, der auf die Oberfläche aufgesprüht wird. Dadurch\nentstehen eine matte, texturierte Oberfläche mit stabilen Merkmalspunkten.\nNach dem Scan kann das Spray einfach mit Wasser oder einem Tuch entfernt\nwerden, ohne das Objekt zu beschädigen.","position":{"start":{"line":154,"column":1},"end":{"line":154,"column":1}},"key":"oXoVYnZ86v"}],"key":"yawKqTcZNh"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":161,"column":1},"end":{"line":161,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Typische Aufnahmefehler","position":{"start":{"line":161,"column":1},"end":{"line":161,"column":1}},"key":"rHooIugMna"}],"identifier":"typische-aufnahmefehler","label":"Typische Aufnahmefehler","html_id":"typische-aufnahmefehler","implicit":true,"key":"eiCzbbCIYL"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":163,"column":1},"end":{"line":164,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In der Praxis treten beim ersten Versuch häufig dieselben Fehler auf. Die\nfolgende Übersicht hilft, diese zu vermeiden:","position":{"start":{"line":163,"column":1},"end":{"line":163,"column":1}},"key":"YBE9zsIl6Q"}],"key":"z6oSTxtHIv"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":166,"column":1},"end":{"line":183,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":166,"column":1},"end":{"line":168,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":166,"column":1},"end":{"line":166,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Zu wenige Fotos oder zu wenig Überlappung","position":{"start":{"line":166,"column":1},"end":{"line":166,"column":1}},"key":"p1MaH9F6v6"}],"key":"kJzNfmg02M"},{"type":"text","value":": Das Modell enthält Lücken oder\neinzelne Bereiche werden gar nicht rekonstruiert. Abhilfe: mehr Fotos\naufnehmen und kleinere Winkelschritte zwischen den Aufnahmen wählen.","position":{"start":{"line":166,"column":1},"end":{"line":166,"column":1}},"key":"rhs3D1jNXy"}],"key":"nrb1z2x369"}],"key":"CHRRFwTlpy"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":169,"column":1},"end":{"line":172,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":169,"column":1},"end":{"line":169,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bewegtes Objekt","position":{"start":{"line":169,"column":1},"end":{"line":169,"column":1}},"key":"GYxEoYrGs9"}],"key":"HCHQKyuWLu"},{"type":"text","value":": Wenn das Objekt zwischen den Aufnahmen leicht verschoben\nwird, zum Beispiel weil es auf einer drehbaren Plattform steht, versagen die\nBerechnungen für die Kamerapositionen. Abhilfe: Das Objekt immer fest\npositioniert lassen, die Kamera bewegen.","position":{"start":{"line":169,"column":1},"end":{"line":169,"column":1}},"key":"qglR2X8qTC"}],"key":"k9twcLvFIp"}],"key":"a2fXCWqPLX"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":173,"column":1},"end":{"line":176,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":173,"column":1},"end":{"line":173,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wechselnde Beleuchtung","position":{"start":{"line":173,"column":1},"end":{"line":173,"column":1}},"key":"TH6SGkUTws"}],"key":"KONw2AZh2J"},{"type":"text","value":": Wenn sich das Licht während der Aufnahme ändert,\nzum Beispiel weil eine Wolke die Sonne verdeckt, entstehen Helligkeitssprünge\nzwischen den Fotos. Abhilfe: Drinnen unter gleichmäßiger Beleuchtung aufnehmen\noder eine kurze, bewölkte Aufnahmesituation wählen.","position":{"start":{"line":173,"column":1},"end":{"line":173,"column":1}},"key":"fr5R5RSWGL"}],"key":"w8dyIUnI3j"}],"key":"JVV4vFpo1d"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":177,"column":1},"end":{"line":179,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":177,"column":1},"end":{"line":177,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Zu glatte oder einfarbige Oberfläche","position":{"start":{"line":177,"column":1},"end":{"line":177,"column":1}},"key":"thG5TnXbnR"}],"key":"kJExBfigeN"},{"type":"text","value":": Der Algorithmus findet keine\nstabilen Merkmalspunkte. Abhilfe: Mattierungsspray oder das Objekt auf einen\nstrukturierten Untergrund legen, der als Referenz dient.","position":{"start":{"line":177,"column":1},"end":{"line":177,"column":1}},"key":"ziumZL6OGz"}],"key":"v7eaey3COe"}],"key":"IJJCPaqwBW"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":180,"column":1},"end":{"line":183,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":180,"column":1},"end":{"line":180,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Zu großer Abstand zur Kamera","position":{"start":{"line":180,"column":1},"end":{"line":180,"column":1}},"key":"zzT2bnnnoT"}],"key":"EL1ULr9Mk0"},{"type":"text","value":": Wenn das Objekt nur einen kleinen Teil des\nBildes einnimmt, gehen Details verloren. Abhilfe: Nah genug herangehen, so\ndass das Objekt mindestens die Hälfte des Bildes füllt.","position":{"start":{"line":180,"column":1},"end":{"line":180,"column":1}},"key":"XLtOGUMOY4"}],"key":"vfrl1bTAzV"}],"key":"ynoqOaHwyu"}],"key":"mEGHUWr9ma"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":184,"column":1},"end":{"line":184,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Zusammenfassung und Ausblick","position":{"start":{"line":184,"column":1},"end":{"line":184,"column":1}},"key":"dyZUPumsD7"}],"identifier":"zusammenfassung-und-ausblick","label":"Zusammenfassung und Ausblick","html_id":"zusammenfassung-und-ausblick","implicit":true,"key":"phVP9kjNHy"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":186,"column":1},"end":{"line":192,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In diesem Kapitel haben wir die wichtigsten Regeln für eine erfolgreiche\nFotoaufnahme für die Photogrammetrie kennengelernt. Konstante\nKameraeinstellungen, ausreichende Überlappung, mehrere Aufnahmeebenen und\nein neutraler Hintergrund sind die Grundvoraussetzungen. Glänzende und\nstrukturlose Oberflächen lassen sich mit Mattierungsspray behandeln. Im\nnächsten Abschnitt lernen wir Meshroom kennen und führen die erste eigene\nRekonstruktion durch.","position":{"start":{"line":186,"column":1},"end":{"line":186,"column":1}},"key":"TkAFLeJNMN"}],"key":"pDBFktOghS"}],"key":"I7pwRpjFFZ"}],"key":"lvYJpIymu5"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}},"footer":{"navigation":{"prev":{"title":"2.1 Grundlagen der Photogrammetrie","url":"/chapter02-sec01","group":"2. Photogrammetrie (von der Kamera zur Punktwolke)"},"next":{"title":"2.3 Meshroom: Erste Schritte","url":"/chapter02-sec03","group":"2. Photogrammetrie (von der Kamera zur Punktwolke)"}}},"domain":"http://localhost:3000"}